bumblebee (3.2.1-94~trustyppa1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Sync debian/copyright with Debian 3.1.2-12
  * Sync debian/control with Debian 3.1.2-12
  * Mention workaround for #822330 in README.Debian
  * Add 358, 361, 364 to blacklist
  * Run autoreconf before building
  * Add fix-typos.patch, errors found by Lintian
  * Add xorg-binary-config.patch for compatibility with xorg-legacy
  * Add ignore-systemd-logind-noise.patch to ignore logind red herring
    messages
  * Add ignore-failure-to-set-DRM-interface.patch to ignore DRM red
    herring messages
  * Install modprobe file in bumblebee/modprobe.d
  * Generate simplified maintainer scripts at build time per-distro
  * Delete modprobe file when bumblebee is removed
  * Drop -dbg package in favour of autogenerated one

